
======================================
 Witchhammer -- Firefox Extension
 Version 1.3
======================================

Witchhammer is a Mozilla Firefox extension that allows you to effeciently search
for bands and albums at http://www.metal-archives.com by selecting some text on a 
webpage, right-clicking your mouse, and selecting the appropriate option.

